line_1: Reckless Ambition, that right onward wends,
line_2: In Pandemonium full of ugly fiends?

line_1: Reckless Ambition, that right onward wends,
line_2: Tho' his wild march o'erthrow both fame and friends,

line_1: Reckless Ambition, that right onward wends,
line_2: Obliquely creeping to his treach'rous ends,
